item.title: CVE-2023-2812|2024-08-02T06:33:05.559Z -- unknown -- ultimate%20dashboard
item.description: The Ultimate Dashboard WordPress plugin before 3.7.6 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
